                <div class="faq-item border border-warm-border rounded-2xl overflow-hidden"><button onclick="toggleFaq(this)" class="w-full flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-5 text-left hover:bg-primary-50/50 transition-colors"><span class="font-semibold text-sm pr-4">What is the 70-credit Diploma in Professional Teaching Practice?</span><i data-lucide="chevron-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-text-muted accordion-icon flex-shrink-0"></i></button><div class="accordion-content"><p class="px-6 pb-5 text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">It's a comprehensive certification earned through Alokito Future Teachers (16.5 cr), Subject Expert Training (14 cr per subject), Teachers Plan modules (5.25 cr each), Shadow Teaching/Internship (15 cr), and diploma assessment & portfolio work.</p></div></div>
                <div class="faq-item border border-warm-border rounded-2xl overflow-hidden"><button onclick="toggleFaq(this)" class="w-full flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-5 text-left hover:bg-primary-50/50 transition-colors"><span class="font-semibold text-sm pr-4">How are Subject Expert credits counted?</span><i data-lucide="chevron-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-text-muted accordion-icon flex-shrink-0"></i></button><div class="accordion-content"><p class="px-6 pb-5 text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">Each subject (English, Science, Inclusive Education, Mathematics) is a separate 14-credit program. Take English = 14 credits. Take English and Science = 28 credits. Each includes a demo class, performance report, and placement support.</p></div></div>
                <div class="faq-item border border-warm-border rounded-2xl overflow-hidden"><button onclick="toggleFaq(this)" class="w-full flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-5 text-left hover:bg-primary-50/50 transition-colors"><span class="font-semibold text-sm pr-4">How are Teachers Plan modules counted?</span><i data-lucide="chevron-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-text-muted accordion-icon flex-shrink-0"></i></button><div class="accordion-content"><p class="px-6 pb-5 text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">Each Teachers Plan module — Leadership, AI in Education, ADHD & Special Needs, Digital Teaching Tools, Professional Communication — is a separate 5.25-credit program at ৳5,000 each. You can take them individually and they all count toward your total.</p></div></div>
                <div class="faq-item border border-warm-border rounded-2xl overflow-hidden"><button onclick="toggleFaq(this)" class="w-full flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-5 text-left hover:bg-primary-50/50 transition-colors"><span class="font-semibold text-sm pr-4">What is the demo class facility?</span><i data-lucide="chevron-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-text-muted accordion-icon flex-shrink-0"></i></button><div class="accordion-content"><p class="px-6 pb-5 text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">After completing Alokito Future Teachers and each Subject Expert program, participants conduct a demo class. You receive a detailed performance report evaluating your teaching, a recording of your demo class, and placement support to help you connect with schools.</p></div></div>
                <div class="faq-item border border-warm-border rounded-2xl overflow-hidden"><button onclick="toggleFaq(this)" class="w-full flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-5 text-left hover:bg-primary-50/50 transition-colors"><span class="font-semibold text-sm pr-4">Can I start with individual programs and upgrade later?</span><i data-lucide="chevron-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-text-muted accordion-icon flex-shrink-0"></i></button><div class="accordion-content"><p class="px-6 pb-5 text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">Absolutely! Credits from individual programs count toward the diploma. When you upgrade, the cost of completed programs is deducted from the diploma package price.</p></div></div>
                <div class="faq-item border border-warm-border rounded-2xl overflow-hidden"><button onclick="toggleFaq(this)" class="w-full flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-5 text-left hover:bg-primary-50/50 transition-colors"><span class="font-semibold text-sm pr-4">How does the shadow teaching work?</span><i data-lucide="chevron-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-text-muted accordion-icon flex-shrink-0"></i></button><div class="accordion-content"><p class="px-6 pb-5 text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">After required coursework, you'll be placed at a partner school for 1 month. You'll observe expert teachers (shadow teaching), gradually teach classes (internship), build your portfolio under mentorship, and earn 15 credits plus an internship certificate.</p></div></div>
                <div class="faq-item border border-warm-border rounded-2xl overflow-hidden"><button onclick="toggleFaq(this)" class="w-full flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-5 text-left hover:bg-primary-50/50 transition-colors"><span class="font-semibold text-sm pr-4">Are programs online or in-person?</span><i data-lucide="chevron-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-text-muted accordion-icon flex-shrink-0"></i></button><div class="accordion-content"><p class="px-6 pb-5 text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">Both online and hybrid. Most coursework is online; demo classes, shadow teaching, and some workshops are in-person.</p></div></div>
